Loading the excel data to the Power BI 7

Follow the outlined steps:

1. Open Power BI Desktop and click on Get data

2. Select Excel File from the options

3. Upload File from your computer

4. Select H-1B NewDesktopexcel

5. Click on Load Data





Follow the link below to learn more on how to Import excel data to Power Bi

https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/power-bi/connect-data/desktop-import-excel-workbooks
